===Verb===
{{irregverb|'''to spoil'''|'''[[spoils]]'''|'''[[spoiled]] '''or''' [[spoilt]]'''|'''[[spoiled]] '''or''' [[spoilt]]'''|'''[[spoiling]]'''}}

#''(transitive)'' To [[ruin]].
#''(transitive)'' To [[coddle]] or [[pamper]] to excess.
#''(intransitive)'' Of food, to become bad, [[sour]] or [[rancid]].

====Synonyms====
